{"tid":178340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(義士）旺暴侍應仔上訴被駁回 即時入獄","createTime":"2017-03-29T13:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T13:13:12.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"611acec524efd0422f499a46fabc3dc041e29c74","tid":178340,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:07:25.000Z","msg":"陳柏洋襲警及拒捕上訴被駁回　即時再監禁<br />\n【Now新聞台】去年的旺角騷亂，熱血公民成員陳柏洋被裁定襲警及拒捕罪成，他就定罪及判刑提出上訴被高等法院駁回，即時重新收監。<br />\n<br />\n陳柏洋到高等法院聽取上訴裁決。<br />\n<br />\n他於去年十月，在九龍城裁判法院被裁定襲警及拒捕罪成，判監九個月，是旺角騷亂首宗被定罪案件。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官拒絕他的上訴保釋申請，到今年一月底，陳柏洋再向高等法院申請保釋才獲批。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=215889\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D215889&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=ef1fa0e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D215889&h=91994b1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=215889</a><br />\n擲水樽都坐九個月  做左義士仲要無人提"},{"pid":"f6d530d477bd6eed8e386e240f9009d780b82178","tid":178340,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:08:45.000Z","msg":"熱血公民成員唔怕，陳雲會教佢申請政治庛護離港"},{"pid":"ea4112fab06cb0ca4c3e0ee44a1f0c99adcf12c1","tid":178340,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:13:12.000Z","msg":"廿秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}